snippet.title: Let's Cook Together - Official Trailer. Cooperative kitchen game for two!
snippet.description:
2 chefs, 1 kitchen and a long counter in the middle - it's the cooperation that makes the dish!

Let’s Cook Together is a cooperative cooking game for two players – adults and children alike – family members, friends and couples. In this restaurant game, you become a pair of quirky chefs who need to communicate and share their tasks to make and serve delicious food.
 
More info: www.cooktogethergame.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LetsCookGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/LetsCookGame
